        </link>
        <updated>2020-12-24T06:13:51.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Gridea官方网站: https://gridea.dev/</p>
<p>1.建立github仓库<br>
1）首先点击&quot;+&quot;好, 新建仓库<br>
<img src="https://xiaoguangge.github.io/post-images/1608790671356.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
2）仓库名为 [用户名.github.io] ，后续就可以用这个仓库名作为<strong>博客访问域名</strong>, 仓库选择公开。<br>
<img src="https://xiaoguangge.github.io/post-images/1608798911638.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
注意：输入的是你未来要访问的URL<br>
3）选择仓库时候，需要新建目录，才能选择，要不会显示为none。<br>
<img src="https://xiaoguangge.github.io/post-images/1608799053976.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://xiaoguangge.github.io/post-images/1608799058460.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
4）创建仓库后点击仓库的settings，拉到页面最端检查自己是否开启了github pages<br>
<img src="https://xiaoguangge.github.io/post-images/1608796360248.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://xiaoguangge.github.io/post-images/1608799325223.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
到这里，就成功建立了内容为空的博客页面，访问域名是你的仓库名。<br>
2.建立github token<br>
点击右上角头像的settings，选择菜单最下面的developer settings<br>
<img src="https://xiaoguangge.github.io/post-images/1608796715975.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
选择personal access tokens，并生成一个新的token<br>
<img src="https://xiaoguangge.github.io/post-images/1608797634319.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
新建token时填完名称后把repo勾选起来，然后到点击生成<br>
<img src="https://xiaoguangge.github.io/post-images/1608797639132.png" alt="" loading="lazy">    生成成功后，建议将你的令牌保存起来，根据提示，你的这个令牌关掉页面后你再也找不到了<br>
3.配置Gridea<br>
<img src="https://xiaoguangge.github.io/post-images/1608799722865.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
4.开启文章评论<br>
点击链接https://github.com/settings/applications/new, 创建<br>
<img src="https://xiaoguangge.github.io/post-images/1608800156674.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://xiaoguangge.github.io/post-images/1608800263862.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
创建完成后可将 Client ID 和 Client Secret 填到Gridea<br>
<img src="https://xiaoguangge.github.io/post-images/1608800716080.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
5.主题<br>
simple主题就很好看<br>
<img src="https://xiaoguangge.github.io/post-images/1608801304453.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
